org.hypergraphdb.storage
Class HGStoreSubgraph

java.lang.Object
  org.hypergraphdb.storage.HGStoreSubgraph
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Pair<HGPersistentHandle,Object>>, StorageGraph
public class HGStoreSubgraph
extends Object
implements StorageGraph

A StorageGraph bound to a HGStore. It's based on a set of root handles and its iterator will traverse the primitive storage graph starting from those roots.

Author:
Borislav Iordanov
